text: Mossie Dowling (born 1946) is a former Irish sportsperson. He played hurling with his local club Kilmallock and with the Limerick senior intra-county team in the 1970s. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Kilmallock hurlers Category:Limerick inter-county hurlers Category:All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship winners Category:1946 births
